cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper is about generative models for image synthesis, specifically focusing on controlling the location and content of objects in the image. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves modeling conditional distributions and controlling object parts, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories.
